description.excerpt: We replace some layers in MobileNet-v1 architecture with lambda layer. It significantly reduces the parameters with some performance gain on cifar100 dataset.

installation.excerpt:
We use the implementation done by `lucidrains <https://github.com/lucidrains/lambda-networks>`_

.. code-block:: bash

   pip install lambda-networks
